---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "DeepSeek 使用技巧目录"
description: "DeepSeek 安装、提示词、接口接入、表格处理和代码阅读等核心教程与参考文章目录。"
keywords: "DeepSeek使用技巧,DeepSeek安装教程,DeepSeek提示词,DeepSeek API"
permalink: /jiqiao/index.html
---
<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow">目录</p>
    <h1>DeepSeek 使用技巧目录</h1>
    <p class="tagline">下方「核心教程」为优先收录内容；更多参考文章供站内阅读，默认不进入搜索引擎索引。</p>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="section">
  <div class="container">
    <h2 style="margin-bottom:20px;">核心教程（可索引）</h2>
    <div class="toc-list">
    {% for post in collections.indexablePosts %}
    <article class="toc-card">
      {% set cardCover = post.data.coverImage or post.data.cover %}
      {% if cardCover %}
      <img src="{{ cardCover | assetUrl }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }} 配图" width="240" height="160" loading="lazy">
      {% endif %}
      <div>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <p class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</p>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
    </div>

    <h2 style="margin:48px 0 20px;">全部参考文章</h2>
    <div class="toc-list">
    {% for post in collections.articles %}
    {% if post.data.generated %}
    <article class="toc-card">
      {% if post.data.cover %}
      <img src="{{ post.data.cover }}" alt="{{ post.data.title }} 配图" width="240" height="160" loading="lazy">
      {% endif %}
      <div>
        <h3><a href="{{ post.url }}">{{ post.data.title }}</a></h3>
        <p>{{ post.data.description }}</p>
        <p class="meta">{{ post.date | readableDate }} · 参考文</p>
      </div>
    </article>
    {% endif %}
    {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
